### Start
    * transmission-daemon

### A torrent or magnet link
    * transmission-remote -a "torrent_link"

### Torrent status
    * transmission-remote -l

### Torrent remove
    * transmission-remote -t all -r
    * transmission-remote -t 3,4 -r

### Web interface
    * Transmission on current computer http://127.0.0.1:9091/
    * Transmission on other computee http://<IP_Address>:9091/

### Stop
    * transmission-remote --exit
